  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study was undertaken to identify prospectively which clinical venous leg ulcer (VLU)
      characteristics known as possible prognostic markers, and which sociodemographic and
      psychologic factors associated with VLU are associated with complete healing at 24 weeks.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
